            <title>[LU-9404] mdt_hsm_add_hal() should avoid settting HSM xattr if HS_EXISTS is already set</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9404</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
